tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trade_executions (
	trade_id UUID,
	timestamp TIMESTAMP,
	quantity INT,
	price DECIMAL
)

CREATE TABLE trade_executions (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE market_activity (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    stock_symbol VARCHAR(255),
    action VARCHAR(50),
    activity_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    trader_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_executions (
    trade_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    quantity DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    execution_type VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
    executed_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    executed_quantity DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trades (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_date TIMESTAMP,
    symbol VARCHAR(50),
    quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE executions (
    execution_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    trade_id INT,
    execution_time TIMESTAMP,
    execution_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    execution_quantity INT
)

CREATE TABLE symbols (
    symbol_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol_name VARCHAR(50),
    symbol_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE market_activity (
    activity_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity_description TEXT
)
CREATE TABLE trades (trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY, symbol VARCHAR(255), quantity INT, price DECIMAL, execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP);
CREATE TABLE traders (trader_id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), email VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE brokers (broker_id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), location VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE markets (market_id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), country VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE executions (execution_id INT PRIMARY KEY, trade_id INT, trader_id INT, broker_id INT, market_id INT, execution_timestamp TIMESTAMP);
